title: december 9: a star war is born
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the making and release of Star Wars: The Last Jedi, which was released today in 2017. She also chats about the debut of a modern music icon. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
